mhegenc will allow the following extensions as per UK profile 1.06 draft 11

Group
-----
- Timers are now an attribute of group rather than scene.

Scene
-----
- AspectRatio is OPTIONAL (no default)

TokenGroup
----------
- TokenGroupItems is OPTIONAL

Stream
------
- Multiplex is OPTIONAL.


New ElementaryActions
=====================

 - SetBackgroundColour
 - SetCellPosition
 - SetFontAttributes
 - SetInputRegister
 - SetTextColour
 - GetFocusPosition
 - SetFocusPosition
 - SetBitmapDecodeOffset
 - GetBitmapDecodeOffset
 - SetVideoDecodeOffset
 - GetVideoDecodeOffset
 - SetSliderParameters

New Events
==========

- FocusMoved
- SliderValueChanged

mhegenc will encode and decode SetDesktopColour and OrigDesktopColour
for the freesat extensions.


mhegenc will also ignore C preprocessor directives.
